div></div></div></div></div><div data-collapse="none" data-animation="default" data-duration="400" data-easing="ease" data-easing2="ease" role="banner" class="navbar-white w-nav"><div class="page-padding"><div class="nav_container"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="nav-logo-link w-nav-brand w--current"><div class="nav_logo-berlitz-wraper-copy"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61ade1765c29d6457e3af12e_berlitz-logo-400x115.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="nav_logo-berlitz"/></div></a><nav role="navigation" class="nav_menu w-nav-menu"><div data-w-id="a3cc97fe-7123-ef47-da9e-4cb0911a4605" class="nav_language"><div class="nav_icon-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61ade1765c29d6f30b3af12c_language-icon-black.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="nav_icon-language-white"/><div class="nav_text-language">EN</div></div><div data-w-id="a3cc97fe-7123-ef47-da9e-4cb0911a460a" class="nav_language-selector"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="nav_english-link w--current">English</a><a href="/de" class="nav_german-link">German</a></div><div class="nav_language-dropdown-wrapper"><div class="nav_lottie-dropdown" data-w-id="a3cc97fe-7123-ef47-da9e-4cb0911a4610" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/619dfeee79684eb82b9e7779/619dfeee79684e7dcd9e77b3_lottieflow-dropdown-easey.json" data-loop="0" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="1" data-is-ix2-target="0" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="2" data-duration="0"></div></div></div></nav><div class="menu-button w-nav-button"><div class="icon-4 w-icon-nav-menu"></div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main-wrapper"><header class="section-header"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-medium"><div class="home-header_heading-wrapper"><div class="margin-vertical margin-large"><h1 class="is-header-h1">Berlitz Insights:<br/>valuable perspectives for<br/>your everyday working life<br/></h1></div></div></div></div></header><section class="section-intro"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-medium"><div class="padding-top"><div class="home-intro_component"><h2 class="text-style-subheader">Berlitz Insights: valuable expert knowledge, completely free of charge.<br/></h2><div class="home-intro_upper-content"><div class="margin-bottom margin-xxlarge"><p class="text-weight-light text-size-medium">Gain valuable insights and practical expert knowledge for your day-to-day work. Our speakers share their experience, best practices and fresh ideas so that you can benefit in the long term.Our webinar series covers a wide range of topics - from artificial intelligence and business skills to B2G training for subsidized measures and information for parents in the Kids &amp; Teens sector.<br/>‍<br/>Berlitz is your partner for training in foreign languages, intercultural know-how and business skills. We offer a range of modern training solutions and support companies with their training strategy.<strong><br/><br/>Join our upcoming 60-minute live webinars: </strong>experience the latest developments in language, soft skills or intercultural trainings and gain insight into our training solutions.<strong><br/><br/>Register now<br/></strong>Participation is free of charge. You will receive your login details via email after registration.<!-- -->‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section-filters"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-medium"><div class="padding-bottom-large"><div class="filters-wrapper jetboost-filter-k9q8"><div class="filters-dropdown-wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid filters-grid"><div data-hover="true" data-delay="0" id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7a5-f8b9d84f" class="filter-dropdown w-dropdown"><div class="webinar-filter w-dropdown-toggle"><div class="w-icon-dropdown-toggle"></div><div>Webinars</div></div><nav class="dropdown-list-filter w-dropdown-list"><div class="filter-form-block w-form"><form id=