etboost-list-wrapper-g16b jetboost-list-wrapper-gdz7 jetboost-list-wrapper-z2x8 jetboost-list-wrapper-zppv w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="w-embed"><input type="hidden" class="jetboost-list-item" value="conflict-communication-23-10-2025" /></div><div class="webinar-card-wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid webinar-card-grid"><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7f8-f8b9d84f" class="webinar-image-card-wrapper"><img alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten.jpg 1382w" class="webinar-image-card"/></div><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7fa-f8b9d84f" class="card-webinar-info-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-heading-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-wrapper"><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="tag-text">Future Skills</div></div></div></div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text">23/10/2025</div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text language">German</div></div></div><h1 class="availability">Heading</h1><h2 class="webinar-card-heading">Conflict Communication</h2></div><div class="description-language-course">Communication is at the heart of interpersonal interactions. But all too often misunderstandings, conflicts and unclear messages lead to tensions. This is where non-violent communication (NVC) according to Rosenberg comes in.</div></div><div class="card-webinar-button-wrapper"><a href="/webinars/conflict-communication-23-10-2025" class="card-webinar-button w-button">Register now</a></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="w-embed"><input type="hidden" class="jetboost-list-item" value="parent-information-session-camps-2026-boost-your-brain---discover-how-cool-languages-are-28-10-2025" /></div><div class="webinar-card-wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid webinar-card-grid"><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7f8-f8b9d84f" class="webinar-image-card-wrapper"><img alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/68501bcc3e93a3fd80a0c3f8_Berlitz%20Webinar%20Page_shutterstock_2441652041_DU.jpg 1750w" class="webinar-image-card"/></div><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7fa-f8b9d84f" class="card-webinar-info-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-heading-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-wrapper"><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="tag-text">Kids &amp; Teens</div></div></div></div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text">28/10/2025</div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text language">German</div></div></div><h1 class="availability">Heading</h1><h2 class="webinar-card-heading">Parent information session: Camps 2026: Boost your brain</h2></div><div class="description-language-course">Learning foreign languages doesn&#x27;t have to be boring cramming - with Berlitz it becomes an adventure! Whether individual training, group course or holiday language camp: our programmes are just as varied as your children&#x27;s interests.</div></div><div class="card-webinar-button-wrapper"><a href="/webinars/parent-information-session-camps-2026-boost-your-brain---discover-how-cool-languages-are-28-10-2025" class="card-webinar-button w-button">Register now</a></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="w-embed"><input type="hidden" class="jetboost-list-item" value="conflict-communication-06-11-2025" /></div><div class="webinar-card-wrapper"><div class="w-layout-grid webinar-card-grid"><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7f8-f8b9d84f" class="webinar-image-card-wrapper"><img alt="" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten.jpg" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398f9090b214e/6728b766122c64bcf9601fe7_Kommuinkation%20in%20Konflikten.jpg 1382w" class="webinar-image-card"/></div><div id="w-node-_8b35dbf3-ac92-3989-7f7b-33e5db84b7fa-f8b9d84f" class="card-webinar-info-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-heading-wrapper"><div class="card-tags-wrapper"><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="w-dyn-item"><div class="tag-text">Future Skills</div></div></div></div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text">6/11/2025</div></div><div class="webinar-tag"><div class="tag-text language">English</div></div></div><h1 class="availability">Heading</h1><h2 class="webinar-card-heading">Conflict Communication</h2></div><div class="description-language-course">Communication is at the heart of interpersonal interactions. But all too often misunderstandings, conflicts and unclear messages lead to tensions. This is where non-violent communication (NVC) according to Rosenberg comes in.</div></div><div class="card-webinar-button-wrapper"><a href="/webinars/conflict-communication-06-11-2025" class="card-webinar-button w-button">Register now</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="navigation" aria-label="List" class="w-pagination-wrapper"></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="Benefits" class="benefits" data-ix="scroll-color-bg-3"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-medium"><div class="padding-vertical-large"><h2 class="benefits-heading">Webinar Highlights</h2><div class="w-layout-grid benefits-grid"><div class="benefit-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61de89ec2ebadebcbceaa028_Remote.svg" width="100" alt="" class="icon-benefit"/><div class="text-benefit">Useful insights into the programs and tips for your organization</div></div><div class="benefit-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61de89ecc1dfb9356c1f1d95_Speaking.svg" width="100" alt="" class="icon-benefit"/><div class="text-benefit">Interactive live webinar with our experienced Berlitz trainers</div></div><div class="benefit-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61e16426ac83482afc1a1e40_61de89ed2b0f2b95256cc567_Colleagues-p-500.png" width="100" alt="" class="icon-benefit"/><div class="text-benefit">International atmosphere with participants from HR and T&amp;D</div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="Testimonial" class="testimomnial"><div class="page-padding"><div class="container-medium"><div class="padding-vertical-large"><div class="testimonial-headings-wrapper"><h1 class="testimonials-heading">What our customers say</h1><p class="testimonial-text">A small selection of references from customers that use our training solutions.<br/></p></div><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="testimonial-slider w-slider" data-autoplay="true" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="true" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true"><div class="w-slider-mask"><div class="testimonial-slide w-slide"><div class="w-layout-grid referral-grid"><div id="w-node-_54b93f20-82f4-dc77-1f58-f01c1d5c7695-f8b9d84f" class="logo-grid-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/64e75e124c15a951ca89c22b_Amazon%20Career%20Choice%20Logo%20Orange.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 941px) 100vw, 941px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/64e75e124c15a951ca89c22b_Amazon%20Career%20Choice%20Logo%20Orange-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/64e75e124c15a951ca89c22b_Amazon%20Career%20Choice%20Logo%20Orange-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/64e75e124c15a951ca89c22b_Amazon%20Career%20Choice%20Logo%20Orange.png 941w" alt="" class="testimonial-logo"/></div><div class="testimonial-rich-text w-richtext"><p>&quot;We are pleased to have Berlitz as an Amazon Career Choice training partner offering our employees first-class language training in different countries. The Berlitz Flex language program offers the flexibility for all employees to decide for themselves when and where they want to learn and receive a learning program tailored to their level. The live coaching sessions with Berlitz trainers are an additional motivation booster for our employees.&quot;</p><blockquote>Amazon Career Choice</blockquote></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-slide w-slide"><div class="w-layout-grid referral-grid"><div id="w-node-_54b93f20-82f4-dc77-1f58-f01c1d5c76a0-f8b9d84f" class="logo-grid-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61e1474dd90fea196516ebdd_Aptiv_Logo.png" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 666px) 100vw, 666px" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61e1474dd90fea196516ebdd_Aptiv_Logo-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61e1474dd90fea196516ebdd_Aptiv_Logo.png 666w" alt="" class="testimonial-logo"/></div><div class="testimonial-rich-text w-richtext"><p>&quot;We have been working successfully with Berlitz for many years now, and have been taking advantage of both their well-organized language courses and their program of in-house seminars. Particular mention should go to the flexibility with which Berlitz responds to all requests and to the degree of customization of all courses that have been held for us, both in the virtual and face-to-face formats.&quot;</p><blockquote>Janine Reinhardt, HR Training Lead Germany and Johannes Bornmüller, HR Director. Aptiv Services Deutschland GmbH</blockquote></div></div></div><div class="testimonial-slide w-slide"><div class="w-layout-grid referral-grid"><div id="w-node-_54b93f20-82f4-dc77-1f58-f01c1d5c76ac-f8b9d84f" class="logo-grid-wrapper"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5e1313965aa398acb80b2113/61e1474eed8a887cd602cc14_APOLLO_LOGO.png" loading="lazy" alt="" class="testimonial-logo"/></div><div class="testimonial-rich-text w-richtext"><p>&quot;We opted for the Berlitz Connect e-learning platform as the perfect complement to our existing face-to-face language learning, since it allows our employees to work on their language skills independently and according to their individual needs. The good coordination of face-to-face and online language instruction is a major advantage of working with Berlitz.&quot;</p><blockquote>Dr. Rüdiger Keller, Apollo-Optik Holding GmbH &amp; Co. KG</blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class="w-slider-arrow-left"><div class="icon-left w-icon-slider-left"></div></div><div class="w-slider-arrow-right"><div class="icon-right w-icon-slider-right"></div></div><div class="slide-nav w-slider-nav w-slider-nav-invert w-round"></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><div id="form" class="contact-form_new"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-22 w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid grid_form_new"><h2 class="form-h2_new">Find out more</h2><div class="form-text-subheader_new">Contact us today – with no obligation on your part. <br/>Your Berlitz team will contact you shortly.</div><div class="code-embed w-embed"><style>
